19
00:01:13,448 --> 00:01:15,778
in this beautiful
place that is so calm,

20
00:01:15,909 --> 00:01:17,409
it gives me this
wonderful illusion

21
00:01:17,494 --> 00:01:19,914
that time is just
standing still.

22
00:01:21,665 --> 00:01:23,755
But then, as both my
work and school life

23
00:01:23,875 --> 00:01:25,585
were starting to get settled,

24
00:01:25,669 --> 00:01:26,999
something drastic happened,

25
00:01:28,255 --> 00:01:32,015
I met them, the girls
who may be my relatives,

26
00:01:34,553 --> 00:01:37,103
Miina Miyafuji,

27
00:01:37,180 --> 00:01:38,350
Karen Onodera.

28
00:01:39,725 --> 00:01:42,445
