36
00:02:03,457 --> 00:02:05,827
One, a stranger.

37
00:02:05,959 --> 00:02:07,999
One, a blood relative.

38
00:02:09,129 --> 00:02:11,089
In that very strange
relationship,

39
00:02:11,173 --> 00:02:14,013
